                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing ferro-molybdenum through combination of hydrogen-based shaft furnace reduction and electric furnace smelting",
                    "氢基竖炉还原和电炉冶炼联合制备钼铁合金的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for preparing ferro-molybdenum through combination of hydrogen-based shaft furnace reduction and electric furnace smelting, which comprises the following steps: (1) mixing fine iron powder with molybdenum oxide powder, bentonite and slaked lime, and pelletizing to obtain green pellets; (2) the green pellets are dried and roasted, and oxidizing pellets are prepared; (3) reducing the oxidized pellets in a hydrogen-rich reduction shaft furnace by adopting hydrogen-rich gas to obtain molybdenum-containing DRI; (4) cooling the molybdenum-containing DRI under the protection of inert gas; and (5) the cooled molybdenum-containing DRI is subjected to electric furnace smelting and melt separation, and the ferro-molybdenum alloy is obtained. According to the method, the ferro-molybdenum alloy is produced in a hydrogen-based shaft furnace-electric furnace smelting mode, so that process energy consumption and pollutant emission are reduced; in the pellet preparation process, slaked lime is added and reacts with molybdenum oxide powder to form a calcium molybdate stable compound, high-temperature volatilization of molybdenum oxide is inhibited, and meanwhile the pelletizing performance of the molybdenum-containing pellets is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氢基竖炉还原和电炉冶炼联合制备钼铁合金的方法，包括下述步骤：（1）将铁精粉粉与氧化钼粉、膨润土、消石灰混合、造球，制得生球；（2）将生球进行干燥、焙烧，制备氧化性球团；（3）所述氧化性球团在富氢还原竖炉中采用富氢气体进行还原，得到含钼DRI；（4）将含钼DRI在惰性气体保护下冷却；（5）将冷却后含钼DRI进行电炉冶炼熔分，获得钼铁合金。本方法采用氢基竖炉‑电炉冶炼的方式生产钼铁合金，减少工序能耗及污染物排放；球团制备过程中添加消石灰，与氧化钼粉反应形成钼酸钙稳定化合物，抑制氧化钼的高温挥发，同时改善含钼球团的造球性能。"
                }
            ]
